
- Stores all persistent data for the Telegram Sticker Counter Bot.
- Tables included:
    • stickers — Tracks sticker counts per user per group.
        - group_id: ID of the group chat.
        - user_id: ID of the user.
        - username: Full name of the user.
        - count: Number of stickers sent by the user in that group.
    • groups — Stores group IDs where the bot is active.
- Automatically created on the first run of bot.py if it doesn't exist.
- Keeps data persistent even if the bot restarts.
- Not included in version control (.gitignore) to avoid conflicts and private data leaks.
